{
  "stem": "13251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, coming from a kosher background, anything that wasn't-- not that it's-- that it's not kosher, I mean, it's just cornflakes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it-- it-- it was like a suspect, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But I remember it was a-- it was different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah, so here we were, all these hundreds of kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how they kept track of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah, we all had these names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were shipped-- taken by train by-- up north.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember they-- they put us in with a-- a family that was almost on top of railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a temporary thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I mean, it was like I could almost touch the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was right on the tracks almost.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, I remember it was a village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- they got-- they have some crazy names in England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was called Shippea Hill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yeah, it's a small little village in North England, probably in Cambridgeshire-- or 'shear'.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we ended up in Ely-- E-L-Y-- which is a small town-- a small city-- 8,000 people it had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we-- and they put us in a boys' home-- a Jewish boys' home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed there for the duration of the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To-- to '46, I think, after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It varied.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we were as high as 60, maybe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a huge house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ely was like country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I guess real estate wasn't that expensive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had this-- they gave us, as a residence, this old house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It was four stories high.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I describe this house to people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It blows their mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had two front entrances, because it was so wide and big.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It had two entrances, OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
